children.text: Holding space while not grabbing an anticucho locks direction.
Only triggers when an anticucho with that UID exists.

parameters.text: Function.Call("eLevel/Movement.is_space_valid", spr_player.grid_x, spr_player.grid_y - 1) & newline & Function.Call("eLevel/Movement.can_move_anticucho", spr_anticucho.UID, "up") & newline & round(time)
